Titolo: Dark Earth (video game)

Anno: 1997

Descrizione: Dark Earth is a post-apocalyptic adventure game with action elements, developed by Kalisto Entertainment and published by MicroProse for Microsoft Windows in 1997. Reviewers were overwhelmingly positive, with critics commenting on the well thought-out story and milieu and the impressive visuals, though the combat was criticized. It was a commercial hit, with 500,000 copies sold by 1999.